Hey everyone,

surf_annoying

This Map Has been made by: WireleZz, Sparkes, Kozine

Difficulty surfing: Easy/Medium skilled.

1 Spawn, 3 Stages, 1 Ending.

Level 1: Surfing into holes, holes will be random each round.
Level 2: You must surf each ramp.
Level 3: 100 holes, only 10 holes possible random each round.

On spawn & on the end are some extras for the players to have a laugh, find it out for yourself ;)
